HEADWORD: Laziness
<hw>La"zi*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
lazy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Laziness</qex> travels so slowly, that Poverty soon overtakes
him.</q> <rj><qau>Franklin.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

